entries.quest_escort_d: Lord Cyssc never travels without his personal bodyguard, The Scale Guard, and by all reports Commander Khrask has joined her Lord for this journey.
entries.quest_escort_t: Commander Khrask and the Scale Guard
entries.quest_location_d: Lord Cyssc will make the for the Planets surface. He must not be allowed to land.
entries.quest_target_d: Lord Cyssc travels in a modified heavy cruiser. Do not expect a simple fight.
entries.title: Space Kashyyyk: Fall of the Black Scale
entries.title_d: Lord Cyssc and his escort have finally arrived in Kashyyyk. Wipe them out and leave no survivors.
